name: Dragcookie
description:
This delicious Dragcookie is a by-product of our Dragcoins Collection.

Dragcoins is a Project of exclusive 3D coins in gold and diamonds found in Opensea. The collection represents the Dragqueens, one of the most influential communities in pop culture.

We minted these Dragcookies on the last day of 2021! There are 57 gift cookies for Dragcoins fans. Another 57 will be minted in 2022 for our owners!

We hope that 2022 will be as sweet for you as our cookie. Cheers!
